ADDITIONAL NOTICE — RESPONSIBLE USE

Nova is an AI-powered emotional support tool. It is not a licensed mental
health service, therapist, counselor, or medical provider. Users of this
software are responsible for ensuring it is used appropriately and that
any deployment includes the required disclaimer:

  "This is not medical or professional advice. If you're going through a
   difficult time, please consider speaking with someone you trust or a
   qualified professional."

Crisis resources must be displayed prominently in any deployment:
- 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline (US): 988
- SAMHSA: 1-800-662-4357
- International: https://findahelpline.com
